    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Techniques: Purple</p><p></p><p>As an action, you can cover your Juggernaut armor in chakra, blending into your surroundings, similar to the Body Camouflage Ninjutsu. </p><p>This lasts until you deactivate it. </p><p>While active, you are considered lightly obscured, and can hide from a creature even when they have a clear line of sight to you. </p><p>Wisdom (Perception) checks to find you that rely on vision are made with disadvantage.</p>",
